flowRoot.flowPara: Adrestia is a turn-based spellcasting strategy game based on behavioral economic principles. Fight for glory on the wizzingfield and become the Graducator!
This book contains holy rituals for the devout. Themes of healing and purity run throughout. They say that eternal life awaits for those who unlock its secrets.
Enemy takes k damage k turns from now for all positive integer k.

g.aria-label: Ironic. He could save others from death, but not himself.

flowRoot.flowPara: Double stroke widths when used as shape outline, since half of the thickness is hidden by the fill.
Small: 16px. For spell labels, detail text
Normal: 24px. For UI elements, small buttons
For emphasis, prefer bold and italic over font size.
Avoid sharp rectangles; make softer with 5px border radius.
Shades: Black and white are staples. Grey deemphasizes.
Pastel: Very faint, nearly white colours that derive most of their apparent hue from their outline. Very light vivids (yellow and green) adjusted to be visible on white.
